com.example.hotpot0.models

Class UserProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.hotpot0.models.UserProfile

  • public class UserProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a user profile stored in Firestore. Firestore handles ID generation unless you manually assign one.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      UserProfile()
      Required empty constructor for Firestore deserialization.
      UserProfile(Context context, java.lang.String name, java.lang.String emailID, java.lang.String phoneNumber)
      Constructs a new UserProfile using provided user details and automatically assigns a device ID via Settings.Secure#ANDROID_ID.
